data.description: ***Seller concessions up to $5,000 with acceptable offer*** This beautiful home is located in Gulf Breeze and boasts an open-concept design that allows plenty of natural light, giving it a spacious feel. With over 2,400 sq ft of living space, this home features 4 generous bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and an oversized office/flex space. The kitchen is sizable and perfect for entertaining. You'll be delighted to know that the house comes with brand new carpets throughout (July 2023), professional repainting in a classic neutral color (Nov 2023), a smart refrigerator, and a full-size washing machine and dryer, making it a move-in ready home. Take your chance to see this beautiful Gulf Breeze home in person - schedule a showing today!
